<h2 class="bold font-l">Sanji's forgotten memory</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Sanji and Pudding share a single kiss that is hidden from view before she wipes his memory of the event. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="xh85x8" data-video-descrip="Serena has one more thing for Ash before she leaves..." data-video-title="Serena kisses Ash" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/xh85x8_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/xh85x8.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/KissingDiscretionShot" data-video-tropename="Kissing Discretion Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/Pokemon" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/xh85x8.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Serena kisses Ash</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="w18adg" data-video-descrip="Bloom and Sky have a romantic moment on the beach and start to kiss, but Belle ruins the moment." data-video-title="Winx Club" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/w18adg_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/w18adg.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/KissingDiscretionShot" data-video-tropename="Kissing Discretion Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/WinxClub" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/w18adg.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Winx Club</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="7fb352" data-video-descrip="Austin and Ally share an unseen first kiss after Ally finally conquers her stage fright." data-video-title="Austin and Ally's first kiss" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/7fb352_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/7fb352.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/KissingDiscretionShot" data-video-tropename="Kissing Discretion Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/AustinAndAlly" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/7fb352.jpg">
